document_data.History:
This spell was created by [[Netheril|Netherese]] [[arcanist]] [[Zwei]] in [[-2579 DR|−2579 DR (1280 NY)]], then known as '''''Zwei's 1st extension'''''. It was the first spell of Netherese origin to survive into the [[Present Age]].<br/>

By the 1360s [[DR]], it was considered uncommon in the magical community in [[Faerûn]],<ref> and also only rarely found in [[Zakhara]].{{AQ-time}}

It fell out of use{{Speculation}} after the [[1372 DR|Year of Wild Magic, 1372 DR]], when experienced spellcasters developed the talent to modify some aspects of their spells, like [[Extend spell|extending the duration]].<ref group="note">3rd edition introduced [[metamagic]] feats, including "Extend spell". The ''[[extension]]'' spells, however, did not appear after 2nd edition.
